00:00:20.686 --> 00:00:23.886
Yes, indeed, you all did an excellent job!

00:00:23.916 --> 00:00:26.346
Excellent work, everyone!

00:00:26.686 --> 00:00:31.716
So earlier today Mametchi came walking by and
I happened to overhear him say to his friends..

00:00:31.746 --> 00:00:32.786
So I wondering, -

00:00:32.816 --> 00:00:37.286
do you guys have any idea what the buildings of
TamagotchiTown mightdo at night when we sleep?

00:00:37.716 --> 00:00:39.286
I've never really thought about it before but -

00:00:39.316 --> 00:00:42.416
I guess they must get pretty lonely
without anyone on the streets to watch.

00:00:42.716 --> 00:00:45.346
They're probably just fast asleep like us-tchi.

00:00:46.446 --> 00:00:48.186
Yeah, as if.

00:00:48.346 --> 00:00:51.186
Sleeping just seems so boring and would be
such a waste of our time!

00:00:51.516 --> 00:00:53.716
Shouldn't they get starting right about now?

00:00:53.746 --> 00:00:55.686
Yup, any minute now.

00:00:55.746 --> 00:00:57.416
Hey, take a look, there's one now!

00:00:57.646 --> 00:00:59.886
It's so delicious-tchi!

00:00:59.946 --> 00:01:02.886
Every night Kuchipatchi has the same dream!

00:01:02.916 --> 00:01:05.316
Oh, have a look at that one, it's so lovely!

00:01:14.016 --> 00:01:18.016
Great work, Super Hero Chama-Girl,
now finish him off with your Minus-4 Beam!

00:01:18.486 --> 00:01:20.546
Good thinking, super-scientist big brother!

00:01:20.586 --> 00:01:24.986
The Super Chama-Girl's most powerful weapon,
the Minus-4 Beam!

00:01:28.016 --> 00:01:29.616
Ah, It's just so enchanting.

00:01:29.646 --> 00:01:32.616
She has the exact same dream as last night again

00:01:32.686 --> 00:01:35.786
Huh? Oh, look! it's Ms. Perfect!

00:01:35.916 --> 00:01:39.246
Ha-ha! Ha-ha! You're all perfect!

